<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Complaint Submitted Successfully</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
        padding: 20px 0;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #198754;
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .logo {
        max-width: 150px;
        height: auto;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .header h1 {
        color: white;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }

      .success-icon {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
      }

      .success-icon::before {
        content: "âœ“";
        display: inline-block;
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        background-color: #198754;
        color: white;
        border-radius: 50%;
        line-height: 60px;
        font-size: 30px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .message {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .message h2 {
        color: #198754;
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .message p {
        color: #666;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .complaint-details {
        background-color: #f0fdf4;
        border: 1px solid #22c55e;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 25px 0;
      }

      .complaint-details h3 {
        color: #198754;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .complaint-id {
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #333;
        background-color: white;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        border: 1px solid #22c55e;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .platform-info {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin: 25px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #22c55e;
      }

      .platform-info h3 {
        color: #198754;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .platform-info p {
        color: #666;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .cta-button {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 30px 0;
      }

      .cta-button a {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #198754;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 30px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }

      .cta-button a:hover {
        background-color: #16a34a;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px 30px;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }

      .footer p {
        color: #666;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
      }

      .footer a {
        color: #198754;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .footer a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      /* Mobile Responsive */
      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        body {
          padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .email-container {
          margin: 0 10px;
          border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .header {
          padding: 20px 15px;
        }

        .header h1 {
          font-size: 24px;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 30px 20px;
        }

        .message h2 {
          font-size: 20px;
        }

        .complaint-details,
        .platform-info {
          padding: 15px;
        }

        .footer {
          padding: 15px 20px;
        }

        .cta-button a {
          padding: 10px 25px;
          font-size: 14px;
        }
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
        .header h1 {
          font-size: 20px;
        }

        .message h2 {
          font-size: 18px;
        }

        .complaint-id {
          font-size: 16px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="header">
        <img src="<%= logoPath %>" alt="Bighil Platform Logo" class="logo" />
        <!--<h1>Bighil Platform</h1>-->
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="success-icon"></div>

        <div class="message">
          <h2>Complaint Submitted Successfully!</h2>
          <p>Dear <%= userName %>,</p>
          <p>
            Thank you for using our Bighil platform. Your complaint has been
            successfully submitted and is now being processed by our team.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="complaint-details">
          <h3>Your Complaint Reference ID:</h3>
          <div class="complaint-id"><%= complaintId %></div>
          <p
            style="
              margin-top: 10px;
              font-size: 14px;
              color: #666;
              text-align: center;
            "
          >
            Please keep this reference ID for your records and future
            correspondence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="platform-info">
          <h3>About Bighil Platform</h3>
          <p>
            Bighil is your trusted digital platform designed to streamline
            complaint management and provide exceptional customer service. We
            are committed to resolving your concerns efficiently and
            transparently.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our dedicated team works around the clock to ensure your voice is
            heard and your issues are addressed promptly. We believe in building
            trust through reliable service and clear communication.
          </p>
          <p>
            You can track the progress of your complaint and access all our
            services through your personal dashboard.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-button">
          <a href="<%= redirectLink %>">Go to Dashboard</a>
        </div>

        <div
          style="
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 25px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
          "
        >
          <p>
            We will keep you updated on the progress of your complaint via email
            and through your dashboard.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you have any urgent questions, please contact our support team.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p><strong>Thank you for choosing Bighil Platform</strong></p>
        <p>
          For support, email us at
          <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>"><%= supportEmail %></a> or
          contact us directly.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 12px; color: #999">
          This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this message.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
